cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG

This paper deals with computer vision and image processing techniques for depth estimation from a single underwater image. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the use of machine learning techniques, which makes cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely categories. The paper also deals with robotics applications, which makes cs.RO (Robotics and Control) a possible category. Finally, the paper involves the use of graphics techniques for image processing, which makes cs.GR (Graphics) a possible category.
